The paper deals with information transmission over channels, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and communication theory (cs.COMM). The use of minimum mean-squared error estimator and Gaussian input distribution suggests a focus on signal processing (cs.SI) and machine learning (cs.MM). The mention of Bussgang's decomposition also indicates a possible connection to statistical learning theory (cs.LG).
